*Loše* se vraćam kući. (I'm coming home poorly.)
*Nisam dobro prošao kroz ispit.* (I didn't do well on the exam.)
*Njegova loša navika je da prerano izlazi.* (His bad habit is to leave too early.)
*Kvalitet je loš.* (The quality is bad.)
*Tvoje ponašanje je loše.* (Your behavior is bad.)
*Razgovor nije išao loše.* (The conversation wasn't going bad.)
*Moje raspoloženje je loše.* (My mood is bad.)